*Smrt* je neizbežna. (Death is inevitable.)

*Smrt* nam nikada neće biti jasna. (Death will never be clear to us.)

Svi želimo da tražimo večni život, ali *smrt* je neumitna. (We all wish to seek eternal life, but death is unavoidable.)

*Smrt* je neizreciva sudbina. (Death is an unspeakable fate.)

Pad sa *smrt* je moguć. (Falling to death is possible.)

Svi mi govorimo o *smrti*, ali ne znamo koliko je zaista strašna. (We all talk about death, but we don't know how terrifying it really is.)

Ljudi se plaše *smrti*, ali ona je deo života. (People are afraid of death, but it is part of life.)

*Smrt* je neminovna i neizbežna. (Death is inevitable and unavoidable.)